will win a free trip to Hartford, Connecticut.

02:56.743 --> 02:59.109
- I thought it was Hawaii.
- No one said Hawaii.

02:59.212 --> 03:01.772
Now let's get stupid
with our first contestant...

03:01.881 --> 03:04.349
- the human garbage disposal!
- <i>[ Applause ]</i>

03:04.450 --> 03:08.409
Ladles and jelly spoons, I will now take
going low to new heights.

03:08.521 --> 03:12.082
I will swallow anything-
and I mean <i>anything</i>-

03:12.192 --> 03:13.887
you people throw.

03:13.993 --> 03:16.359
- Here, take this!
- <i>[ All Shouting ]</i>

03:16.462 --> 03:19.090
[ Coughs ]
Please, no more spark plugs.

03:19.199 --> 03:21.531
Lisa, would you like a penny
to throw at your brother?

03:21.634 --> 03:24.728
