- You.

04:14.320 --> 04:16.652
Hmm. Well, no one's
forcing you to stay.

04:16.755 --> 04:20.522
- Okay, I'm leaving.
- Hup. You're not going anywhere, missy.

04:20.627 --> 04:22.822
